<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Enlargement" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Enlargement,</orth> 1) release from confinement: <cit><quote>give e. to the swain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 5</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>for e. striving,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 31</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.30" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.6.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 6, 5</bibl>.<lb />2) liberty: <cit><quote>you are curbed from that e. by the consequence of the crown,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 2.3.125" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 3, 125</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>